==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Occulted
<hw>Oc*cult"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Hidden;
secret.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>Concealed by the intervention
of some other heavenly body, as a star by the moon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Occulting</ent>⟦br⟧
